  "info": {
    "name": "Mobile Repair Shop API",
    "description": "API Documentation for Mobile Repair Shop Management System\n\n## Features\n- Authentication & Authorization with JWT\n- User Management\n- Company Management\n- Product/Inventory Management\n- Sales Management\n- Service/Repair Management\n\n## Getting Started\n1. Use the environment file for this collection\n2. Call POST /auth/signin to login\n3. Token will be saved automatically\n4. Use other endpoints with auto-authentication",
